\par\pard\plain \fi360\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 a. Abraham is called \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93the friend of God\u8221\'94 three times, two times in the Old Testament and one time in the New Testament.}
\par\pard\plain \tx1080\li1080\fi-360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8658\'3F\tab Jehoshaphat, the king of Judah, said this in one of his prayers to God:}
\par\pard\plain \li1440\fi360\ri360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Art not thou our God, who didst drive out the inhabitants of this land before thy people Israel, and gavest it to the seed of Abraham thy friend for ever?\u8221\'94 (2 Chr. 20:7)}{\f0\fs24 .}
\par\pard\plain \tx1080\li1080\fi-360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8658\'3F\tab God Himself said this to Israel:}
\par\pard\plain \li1440\fi360\ri360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But thou, Israel, art my servant, Jacob whom I have chosen, the seed of Abraham my friend\u8221\'94 (Is. 41:8)}{\f0\fs24 .}
\par\pard\plain \tx1080\li1080\fi-360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8658\'3F\tab James the writer of the New Testament book said this:}
\par\pard\plain \li1440\fi360\ri360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93And the scripture was fulfilled which saith, Abraham believed God, and it was imputed unto him for righteousness: and he was called the Friend of God\u8221\'94 (Js. 2:23)}{\f0\fs24 .}
\par\pard\plain \fi360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 b. Jesus Christ Himself deliberately said that His followers were }{\f0\fs24\i1 His friends}{\f0\fs24 .}
\par\pard\plain \li1440\fi360\ri360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ye are my friends, if ye do whatsoever I command you. Henceforth I call you not servants; for the servant knoweth not what his }{\f0\fs24\b1\scaps Lord}{\f0\fs24\b1  doeth: but I have called you friends; for all things that I have heard of my Father I have made known unto you\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 (Jn. 15:14\endash 15)}{\f0\fs24 .\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  Leadership Ministries Worldwide. (1996). \\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/posbkjv01ge2?ref=Bible.Ge18.1&off=262&ctx=ship+of+man+to+God.%0a~a.+Abraham+is+called"}{\fldrslt\f2\fs24\b0\i1\ul\ulc0\cf3 Genesis (Chapters 12\endash 50)\\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  (Vol. II, p. 89). Chattanooga, TN: Leadership Ministries Worldwide.\\end_Scrv_fn\}}
