\par\pard\plain \ltrch\loch {\f0\fs32\b1 2}{\f0\fs24  (18:1\endash 2) }{\f0\fs24\b1 Meditation\hich\f0 \emdash \loch\f0 Prayer}{\f0\fs24 : How can we become a friend of God? Meditate and pray\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  Leadership Ministries Worldwide. (1996). \\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/posbkjv01ge2?ref=Bible.Ge18.1-2&off=2827&ctx=ith+me%E2%80%9D+(Re.+3:20).%0a~2+(18:1%E2%80%932)+Meditatio"}{\fldrslt\f2\fs24\b0\i1\ul\ulc0\cf3 Genesis (Chapters 12\endash 50)\\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  (Vol. II, p. 89). Chattanooga, TN: Leadership Ministries Worldwide.\\end_Scrv_fn\}}
