\par\pard\plain \li720\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 Thought 1}{\f0\fs24 . The point is this: meditation and prayer are the way to draw closer to God, the way to become a close, intimate friend with God.}
\par\pard\plain \tx1080\li1080\fi-360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24 (1)\tab Meditation draws us closer to God.}
\par\pard\plain \li1440\fi360\ri360\sb180\qj\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But know that the }{\f0\fs24\b1\scaps Lord}{\f0\fs24\b1  hath set apart him that is godly for himself: the }{\f0\fs24\b1\scaps Lord}{\f0\fs24\b1  will hear when I call unto him. Stand in awe, and sin not: commune with your own heart upon your bed, and be still. Selah\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8221\'94 (Ps. 4:3\endash 4)}{\f0\fs24 .\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  Leadership Ministries Worldwide. (1996). \\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://ref.ly/logosres/posbkjv01ge2?ref=Bible.Ge18.1-2&off=3927&ctx=een+doing+the+same.%0a~Thought+1.+The+point"}{\fldrslt\f2\fs24\b0\i1\ul\ulc0\cf3 Genesis (Chapters 12\endash 50)\\end_Scrv_fn\}\{\\Scrv_fn=}}{\f1\fs24\b0\i0  (Vol. II, p. 90). Chattanooga, TN: Leadership Ministries Worldwide.\\end_Scrv_fn\}}
